    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are explicitly scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 5 requirements for MRL 2, with documented justification for each. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The assessment supports pre-market submission use. Decision is Accepted with medium assurance level consistent with MRL 2 classification.",
